        "text": "4. Let $f ( x )$ be a real measurable function defined on $[ a , b ]$ . Let $n ( y )$ be the number of solutions of the equation $f ( x ) = y$ . Prove that $n ( y )$ is a measurable function on $\\mathbb { R }$ . ",
