            "6. Let $\\mathbb { R } _ { + } ^ { n } = \\left\\{ x = ( x _ { 1 } , x _ { 2 } , . . . , x _ { n } ) \\in \\mathbb { R } ^ { n } | x _ { n } > 0 \\right\\}$ . Show that the formula "
